name: alloc::collections::btree::fix::<impl collections::btree::node::NodeRef<collections::btree::node::marker::Owned, K, V, collections::btree::node::marker::LeafOrInternal>>::fix_right_border_of_plentiful
doc:
Stocks up any underfull nodes on the right border of the tree.
 The other nodes, those that are neither the root nor a rightmost edge,
 must be prepared to have up to MIN_LEN elements stolen.
